  .actualites
    - @actualites.each do |actu|
      .col-sm-6.actu
        .col-sm-6.case
          = link_to image_tag(actu.image, class: "img-responsive center-block"), actualite_path(actu)

        .col-sm-6.case
          %h3= link_to actu.titre, actualite_path(actu)
          %p
